<style type="text/css">
@import url(http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Antic+Slab);

html,body {
	height:100%;
	margin-top: 0px;
}

h1 {
	font-family: 'Titillium Web', sans-serif;
	font-size:80px;
	color:#ffffff;
}

.lead {
	color:#ffffff;
}


/* Custom container */
.container-full {
	margin: 0 auto;
	width: 100%;
	min-height:100%;
	background-color: #1a4055;

	color:#eee;
	overflow:hidden;
}

.container-full a {
	color:#efefef;
	text-decoration:none;
}

.v-center {
	margin-top:7%;
}
.sliding_background{
	position: absolute;
	background:url(<%= asset_path 'background.jpg' %>) repeat-x;
	height: 315px;
	width: 100%;
}
.js-video {
  height: 0;
  padding-top: 25px;
  padding-bottom: 67.5%;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
 
.js-video.widescreen {
  padding-bottom: 57.25%;
}
 
.js-video.vimeo {
  padding-top: 0;
}

</style>
<div class="sliding_background">&nbsp</div>
<div class="container-full">

	<div class="row">

		<div class="col-lg-12 text-center v-center">

			<p><%= image_tag "logo.png" %></p>

			<br><br>


			<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
				<%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
				<div class="form-group">
					<%= f.email_field :email, class: "form-control input-lg", placeholder: "Enter your email address" , :autofocus => true %></div>
					<div class="form-group">
						<%= f.password_field :password, class: "form-control input-lg", placeholder: "Enter your password"%></div>

						<div class="form-group"><%= f.submit "Sign in", class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" %></div>
						<% if devise_mapping.rememberable? -%>

						<div class="form-group"><%= f.check_box :remember_me %> <%= f.label :remember_me %></div>
						<% end -%>
						<% end %>
						<div class="form-group">
							<%= link_to "Create account", new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block" %>
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4 text-center ">
						<div class="js-video widescreen vimeo">
							<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/87525194" width="100%" height="100%" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>


			</div> <!-- /row -->


			<br><br><br><br><br>

		</div> <!-- /container full -->

		<div class="container">

			<hr>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-12">
				<h2>Set up your event and add people.</h2>
				<p><center><%= image_tag "add_users.jpg" %></center></p>
				<br/>

						<div>First thing you should do after creating an event is adding some participants. You can do it by clicking <%= image_tag "add_person_button.jpg" %> button on your dashboard. After adding few people take a look on your <strong>Debts Statistics</strong> table. Every person will show up with current balance zero. Next thing you can do is to add some <strong>transaction</strong>.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<br/>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-12">
				<h2>Add some transactions.</h2>
				<p><center><%= image_tag "add_transaction.jpg" %></center></p>
				<br/>

						<div>When you have some people on the list, you can add transactions. Transaction is a purchase of some goods. You can select who pays for them and who should be charged for them in the statistics.<br/> <strong>For example:</strong><br/>
						There are 4 people - James, John, Nathan and Sidney. You've bought some common food.James paid 200 and John paid 100. John is not going to eat it, so he should not be charged for that.<br/>
						In that situation you should check only James, Nathan and Sidney names. Then type "200" next to James and "100" next to John (because they were the ones who paid).
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-12">
					<br/>
				<h2>Make some changes when you want.</h2>

						<div>You can add a participant in every moment. When a person comes up and he wants to join your event, you can just add him to the list and check his name in the transactions you already created.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-12">
.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>



		<script type='text/javascript' src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.min.js"></script>


		<script type='text/javascript' src="http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>




		<!-- JavaScript jQuery code from Bootply.com editor -->

		<script type='text/javascript'>

		$(document).ready(function() {

		function animateBackground(){
				$('.sliding_background').animate({
			  'background-position-x': '+=839',
			}, 30000, 'linear', animateBackground );
			}

			animateBackground();

		});

		</script>
